title: Lewis_S08E01_-_Entry_Wound.m4v
description: This is the first episode from the eighth series of Inspector Lewis. This is from PBS which presents both half-episodes shown on ITV with a single larger show. Lewis comes out of retirement to help Hathaway in the first murder case he handles as a DI. The episode begins with an arson case but there quickly follows the murders Hathaway, his assistant and Lewis need to solve
